            <bdt class="style-1204"></bdt>
            <bdt class="style-1205">Idaho</bdt>
            <bdt class="style-1206"></bdt><span class="style-1207">, and the Parties hereby consent to, and waive all <bdt class="style-1208"></bdt>defenses<bdt class="style-1209"></bdt> of lack of personal jurisdiction, and forum non conveniens with respect to venue and jurisdiction in such<bdt class="style-1210"></bdt> state and federal courts<bdt class="style-1211"></bdt>. Application of the United Nations Convention on Contracts for the International Sale of Goods and the Uniform Computer Information Transaction Act (UCITA) are excluded from these Legal Terms.</span>
